trans-unit.source: The URL generation process percent encodes non-alphanumeric characters. So there is no risk that malicious/invalid characters are part of the URL. The only character within an URL that must be escaped in html is the ampersand ("&") which separates query params. So we cannot mark the URL generation as always safe, but only when we are sure there won't be multiple query params. This is the case when there are none or only one constant parameter given. E.g. we know beforehand this will be safe: - path('route') - path('route', {'param': 'value'}) But the following may not: - path('route', var) - path('route', {'param': ['val1', 'val2'] }) // a sub-array - path('route', {'param1': 'value1', 'param2': 'value2'}) If param1 and param2 reference placeholder in the route, it would still be safe. But we don't know.
trans-unit.target: URL生成过程对非字母数字字符进行编码。因此，不存在恶意/无效字符成为URL一部分的风险。 URL中必须在html中转义的唯一字符是用于分隔查询参数的“＆”号。因此，我们不能将URL生成标记为始终安全，只有当我们确定不会有多个查询参数时才将其标记为始终安全。当没有或只有一个常数参数时就是这种情况。例如，我们事先知道这将是安全的：-path（'route'）-path（'route'，{'param'：'value'}）但以下内容可能不正确：-path（'route'，var）-path （'route'，{'param'：['val1'，'val2']}）//子数组-path（'route'，{'param1'：'value1'，'param2'：'value2'}）如果param1和param2在路由中引用了占位符，则仍然是安全的。但是我们不知道。

trans-unit.source: The denormalization first looks at the constructor of the given class to see if any of the parameters have the same name as one of the properties. trans-unit.source: The denormalization first looks at the constructor of the given class to see if any of the parameters have the same name as one of the properties. The constructor is then called with all parameters or an exception is thrown if any required parameters were not present as properties. Then the denormalizer walks through the given map of property names to property values to see if a setter method exists for any of the properties. If a setter exists it is called with the property value. No automatic denormalization of the value takes place.
trans-unit.target: 正则化首先查看给定类的构造函数,看是否有任何参数与属性名称相同。然后使用所有参数调用该构造函数,如果有任何所需参数没有作为属性出现,则抛出异常。然后,正则化器通过给定的属性名到属性值的映射,查看是否存在任何属性的setter方法。如果存在一个setter方法,那么它就会被调用该属性值。值的自动去归一化不会发生。
